data.description: Charming home on .36-acre lot. Living room/dining room combo. Kitchen w/ a trendy touch w/ open shelving. 3 bedrooms w/ hardwood floors. Office w/ large windows. Laundry room w/ sink & shelving & detached garage for storage space. Front yard w/ shade trees & RV parking. Fenced backyard w/ tool shed & covered patio. Home is conveniently located close to restaurants, shopping centers, parks, and schools, w/ easy access to 99E for effortless commuting.
